        "action": "Ban yearly increases while in a committed contract.",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "To stop yearly increases to customers direct debits while in a committed contract. I.e. Mobile phones, gas, electric etc. People have multiple direct debit commitments and when every company increases the amount needed this can be a lot more out of their budget they may not be able to reach to.",
